%% 6. Task Creation Sequence Diagram
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server
    participant Database

    User->>Browser: Click 'Create Task'
    Browser->>Server: POST /tasks
    Server->>Server: Validate input
    alt valid
        Server->>Database: INSERT task record
        Database-->>Server: Task created
        Server-->>Browser: 201 Created
        Browser-->>User: Show success message
    else invalid
        Server-->>Browser: 400 Validation error
        Browser-->>User: Show validation message
    end
```

